**Start from** Lindale Village centre and climb up through the woods to Hampsfell, and the hospice. Then dropping down into Cartmel village. Leave the village via the racecourse, and head vaguely north-westish over Grassgarth heights before dropping down to the River Leven (Windermere's waste waterpip) and ending at the village of Greenodd.

